p.seg:
With these witnesses: the lord William of Mordington; the lord Alan of Swinton;
                  the lord Adam of Prenderguest; Walter, Andrew, Alexander of
                  Paxton; Welliam, vicar of Oldcambus; Robert, son of Gregory;
                  Adam of Little Reston; Bertram, his son; John, son of Elias
                  of Over Ayton; Maurice, son of Merlin; Ralph, grieve of
                  Coldingham; and many others.
